---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/base-layout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Srini.pro - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Srini.pro collects, uses, discloses, and otherwise handles your personal information when you visit and interact with our website and services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>The site collects "personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you," including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Contact details</li>
          <li>Address</li>
          <li>Payment information</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Srini.pro uses collected data to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Notify users of policy changes</li>
          <li>Provide customer support</li>
          <li>Improve services</li>
          <li>Process course enrollments and access</li>
          <li>Send course materials and updates</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <p>The organization states it "will take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that your data is treated securely."</p>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. However, we acknowledge that "no method of transmission over the Internet...is 100% secure," limiting our security guarantees.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Cookies & Tracking</h2>
        <p>The site employs cookies and tracking technologies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Monitor website activity</li>
          <li>Track browser information</li>
          <li>Collect device identifiers</li>
          <li>Provide analytics and improve user experience</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>The privacy policy explicitly states: "We do not share your data with any third party organization nor we sell your personal data to anyone."</p>
        <p>Personal data may only be disclosed if required by law or to protect Srini.pro's rights and property.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Account holders can:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Request export of their personal data</li>
          <li>Request erasure of their data (except where legally or administratively required)</li>
          <li>Update their personal information</li>
          <li>Control communication preferences</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Legal Disclosures</h2>
        <p>Personal data may be disclosed if required by law, court order, or governmental authority to protect the safety, rights, and property of Srini.pro and our users.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices. Please review their privacy policies separately.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Users with privacy concerns or data requests can reach out at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email: contact@srini.pro</strong></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Policy Changes</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12">Last Updated: June 23, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
